item.title: DR WENDY CHRISTIEN - Natural Allergy Relief: Probiotics, Nasal Irrigation & Antihistamine Foods That Work
item.description: This final installment in a series on managing seasonal allergies naturally focuses on the gut-allergy connection and practical remedies. Learn how to choose the right probiotics, as fermented foods like yogurt, kefir, and sauerkraut can either help or worsen symptoms depending on their histamine levels.
